  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients with chronic cancer pain

          -  between 20-80 years old age

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  the presence of severe systemic disease(cardiac, pulmonary, hepatic or renal)

          -  psychiatric or neurologic disease

          -  unable to communicate verbally

          -  nausea and vomiting

          -  patient's refusal
      </textblock>
